# OneDrive Integration Environment Variables

# Microsoft Azure App Client ID
# Get this from https://portal.azure.com/#blade/Microsoft_AAD_RegisteredApps/ApplicationsListBlade
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here

# Microsoft Azure App Client Secret
# Get this from https://portal.azure.com/#blade/Microsoft_AAD_RegisteredApps/ApplicationsListBlade
MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://portal.azure.com/#blade/Microsoft_AAD_RegisteredApps/ApplicationsListBlade
# 2. Create a new app registration or select an existing one
# 3. Note the Application (client) ID
# 4. Create a new client secret under "Certificates & secrets"
# 5. Add the OAuth2 redirect URI under "Authentication": http://localhost:3000/api/auth/onedrive/callback
# 6. Grant the following Microsoft Graph API permissions under "API permissions":
#    - Files.Read
#    - Files.ReadWrite
#    - Files.Read.All
#    - Files.ReadWrite.All
#    - offline_access
# 7. Grant admin consent if required by your organization
